<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak 3 tbsp dried shrimps in 125 ml boiling water for 10 m, then drain keeping the water]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add 440ml water to prawn water if using or 500ml water if not, and cook 330g rice in it for 16m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[blanch 90 g corn kernel and 75 g peans for 2 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[fry 2 beaten eggs without stirring until lightly set, then break up with spatula and set aside]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[stir fry, high heat: 90 g diced ham or bacon, 60 g diced onion 1 chili, then set aside]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when rice is ready, stir fry shrimps, ham, egg, veg, 1 tbp soy sauce then add the rice and cook until done]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
